{"type": "root", "attrs": {"icon": "SOP/shatter", "tags": "model"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Shatter"], "extent": [33, 45]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Shatters the input geometry into multiple pieces."], "extent": [45, 103]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [103, 118], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This tool cuts a model along a jagged line multiple times to create pieces you can then use with the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdfracturedobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Fractured Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdfracturedobject"}, " or ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdglueobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Glue Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdglueobject"}, ". "], "extent": [118, 318]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdfracturedobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Fractured Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdfracturedobject"}, " and ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdglueobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Glue Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdglueobject"}, " tools set up the dynamic relationships between objects. The shatter tool creates the pieces automatically so you don\u2019t have to manually break up the geometry."], "extent": [318, 578]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/break", "type": "link", "text": ["Break"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/break"}, " tool creates a single jagged cut with manual control, whereas this tool creates several automatic cuts."], "extent": [578, 710]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["If you want the object to simply shatter on impact, a quick solution is to use the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/shelf/makebreakable", "type": "link", "text": ["Make Breakable"], "fullpath": "/shelf/makebreakable"}, " tool on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Rigid Bodies"]}, " tab of the shelf. It uses the same voronoi fracture method as the Shatter tool, but gives you less artistic control. It is better to use Shatter for foreground shots and ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/shelf/makebreakable", "type": "link", "text": ["Make Breakable"], "fullpath": "/shelf/makebreakable"}, " for objects in the background."], "extent": [710, 1100]}]}, {"level": 2, "id": "includeme", "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Using Shatter"], "extent": [1100, 1132], "body": [{"type": "ord_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Select the object you want to shatter."], "extent": [1132, 1183]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Click the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "SOP/shatter", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/SOP/shatter"}, {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/voronoifracture", "type": "link", "text": ["Shatter"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/voronoifracture"}, " tool on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Model"]}, " tab."], "extent": [1183, 1284], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": [{"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/shelf/shatter.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "extent": [1284, 1331]}], "container": true}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Modify the parameters of the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/voronoifracture", "type": "link", "text": ["Voronoi Fracture SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/voronoifracture"}, " to customize the way the object shatters. For example, turn off ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Create Inside Surfaces"]}, " if the object is hollow like a jar, or turn it on if the object is solid like a rock."], "extent": [1331, 1592]}], "container": true}]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["See ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/examples/nodes/dop/rbdfracturedobject/ShatterDebris", "type": "link", "text": ["this example file"], "fullpath": "/examples/nodes/dop/rbdfracturedobject/ShatterDebris"}, "."], "extent": [1592, 1671]}], "title": ["Shatter"], "summary": ["Shatters the input geometry into multiple pieces."]}